---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Nieuserver.online | Premium Game Server Hub</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #2a2a2a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1639762681057-408e52192e55?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 350px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 0 20px;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        
        .card {
            background: #383838;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 50px 0;
            border: 1px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .card h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #4CAF50;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .card p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #b0b0b0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            margin-top: 60px;
            border-top: 3px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        nav {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        nav ul li {
            margin: 8px 20px;
        }
        
        nav ul li a {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #4CAF50;
            background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1);
        }
        
        .active {
            color: #4CAF50;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .pixel-divider {
            height: 4px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                90deg,
                #4CAF50,
                #4CAF50 10px,
                transparent 10px,
                transparent 20px
            );
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            background: #2a2a2a;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        
        .tech-stack {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .tech-item {
            background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #4CAF50;
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 20px;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background: #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .timeline-date {
            color: #ff9800;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .timeline-content {
            background: #2a2a2a;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                height: 280px;
            }
            
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            
            .card {
                padding: 30px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/minecraft">Minecraft</a></li>
            <li><a href="/terraria">Terraria</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about" class="active">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    
    <header>
        <h1>The Nieuserver.online Story</h1>
        <p>Where technology meets passion for gaming</p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>Nieuserver.online was born from a simple idea: to create the most reliable and user-friendly hub for game server management. We recognized that players deserve more than just serversâ€”they deserve a complete ecosystem that enhances their gaming experience.</p>
            <p>This website serves as the control center for our gaming community, offering real-time server analytics, community tools, and seamless access to our growing network of game worlds.</p>
            
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Unified Dashboard</h3>
                    <p>Monitor all your favorite servers from one intuitive interface with cross-game statistics and notifications.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Smart Monitoring</h3>
                    <p>Our proprietary monitoring system checks server health every 30 seconds, with automated alerts for any issues.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Community Integration</h3>
                    <p>Built-in tools for player communication, event planning, and shared achievements across all servers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pixel-divider"></div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Technical Excellence</h2>
            <p>Behind the scenes, we've built a robust infrastructure designed for performance and scalability:</p>
            
            <div class="tech-stack">
                <span class="tech-item">Cloudflare CDN</span>
                <span class="tech-item">Docker Containers</span>
                <span class="tech-item">Node.js Backend</span>
                <span class="tech-item">WebSocket API</span>
                <span class="tech-item">Redis Caching</span>
                <span class="tech-item">PostgreSQL</span>
            </div>
            
            <p>Our architecture handles 10,000+ concurrent users with sub-second response times, even during peak gaming hours. The website automatically scales resources based on demand, ensuring consistent performance worldwide.</p>
            
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Global Edge Network</h3>
                    <p>Content delivered through 200+ edge locations for low-latency access worldwide.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Zero-Downtime Updates</h3>
                    <p>Blue-green deployment strategy ensures uninterrupted service during maintenance.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Enterprise Security</h3>
                    <p>End-to-end encryption, DDoS protection, and daily vulnerability scans.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pixel-divider"></div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Our Evolution</h2>
            <p>The journey of Nieuserver.online reflects our commitment to continuous improvement:</p>
            
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-date">January 2024</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <p>Initial concept development and infrastructure planning. Launched first prototype with basic server status monitoring.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-date">June 2024</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <p>Major redesign introducing the unified dashboard. Reached 1,000 active users with our Minecraft integration.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-date">November 2024</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <p>Terraria server support added. Implemented real-time player tracking across all servers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-date">March 2025</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <p>Launched mobile-responsive interface and progressive web app capabilities.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>Today, we process over 50,000 daily requests from players across 15 countries, with plans to expand our server locations and game support throughout 2025.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pixel-divider"></div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Future Roadmap</h2>
            <p>We're constantly evolving to serve our community better. Here's what's coming next:</p>
            
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Mobile App</h3>
                    <p>Native iOS/Android applications for server management on the go.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>API Access</h3>
                    <p>Developer tools for custom integrations and third-party apps.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Mod Marketplace</h3>
                    <p>One-click mod installation with version control for supported games.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Have suggestions? We actively incorporate community feedback into our development cycle.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 <span style="color: #4CAF50; font-weight: bold;">nieuserver.online</span></p>
        <p>Engineered for gamers, by gamers</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>